                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260406-292-victim1574 t18260406-292-viclabel1572"></join>. I was at work with the prisoner at Mr. Irbert's yard, <placeName id="t18260406-292-crimeloc1573">Forum-street, Berkeley-square</placeName>
